  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa13">
<l>puḷḷiṉ vāy kīṇṭāṉaip pollā varakkaṉaik</l>
<l>kiḷḷik kaḷaintāṉaik kīrtti mai pāṭip pōyp</l>
<l>piḷḷaikaḷ ellārum pāvaik kaḷampukkār</l>
<l>veḷḷi yeḻuntu viyāḻam uṟaṅkiṟṟu</l>
<l>puḷḷum cilampiṉa kāṇ pōtarik kaṇṇiṉāy</l>
<l>kuḷḷak kuḷirak kuṭaintu nīrāṭātē</l>
<l>paḷḷik kiṭattiyō. pāvāy. nī naṉ ṉāḷāl</l>
<l>kaḷḷam tavirntu kalantēlōr empāvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heading towards the meeting-place [for] the pāvai-vow</l>
<l>All the girls have reached [it], singing the glories</l>
<l rend="indent">of Him who split [open] the bird’s beak,</l>
<l rend="indent">of Him who nipped off and weeded out the evil Rākṣasa.</l>
<l>Venus has risen, Jupiter has gone to sleep.</l>
<l>See, even the birds are chirping,</l>
<l>O girl with lotus eyes [that resemble] the deer’s!</l>
<l>O girl! Have you been staying in bed without bathing,</l>
<l>diving deep [in the water] so that it is intensely cold?</l>
<l>Oh, on this good day, avoiding deception, join [us].</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
